Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵物就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還是一樣傻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
